{"tid":1485909,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【逆權運動】黑衣人下午秘坐警車 和平集會結束晚上拉隊「入籠」","createTime":"2019-08-18T17:11:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T17:39:30.000Z","uid":120760,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b3a6167afe67841a16606bea272507d3d02c6d2f","tid":1485909,"uid":120760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:11:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190819/59945944\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190819%2F59945944&d=T%2BmtXVGNOTzTHFJD9Tq3cSRJil42CLA7NmQUB0MJ4tY%3D&h=37146476\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190819%2F59945944&h=496d7a46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190819/59945944</a><br />\n<br />\n2014年時任署理保安局局長的李家超，回應有便衣探員煽動衝擊立法會的指控時，曾稱警方「無一個措施叫警員扮示威者或者任何角色」，惟5年後，多名身穿黑衣、持有警棍的男子8.11在銅鑼灣假扮示威者再誘捕；警務處副處長（行動）鄧炳強直認警察「會喬裝成不同人物」， 聲稱其卧底絶不會不符合相關指引。8.18的民陣集會似乎又要提防「卧底」黑罩警假扮抗爭者，滲透遊行隊伍。晚上留守者逐漸散去，有人發現十多名留守者衣着的男子循正門走進警察總部內。《蘋果》已向警察公共關係科查詢，惟至凌晨仍未回覆。<br />\n<br />\n沙田區議員趙柱幫下午在facebook發帖，指8.18「差佬又開始喬裝假扮示威者」。從圖片可見，警車內有至少兩名帶上黑色口罩、身穿黑衣的人，當中有人更坐在司機位，負責駕車；他們四處張望，十分警覺。若他們並非坐在警車，也輕易令人以為他們是抗爭者。趙柱幫呼籲遊行人士與相熟朋友結伴同行，注意安全。<br />\n晚上留守者陸續散去，有市民於晚上11時50分在灣仔警總外，看到事多名身穿白衣黑褲，並戴上口罩的男子，循水馬旁的閘門進入警察總部，質疑警方再次派員喬裝示威者。<br />\n<br />\n以後大家一齊喊<br />\n&quot;一齊走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，留低狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&quot;<br />\n等留底o係現場果班狗好似報導咁自己入返籠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30742eaa97f72c744384dadfc87975430d92f14f","tid":1485909,"uid":50779,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:11:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"86f69e4ff5723fde5dd8ba23ebde148415b91514","tid":1485909,"uid":120760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:17:09.000Z","msg":"自推一下"},{"pid":"8f906e4703db80b1ebc5cd7f932de958e2756fe5","tid":1485909,"uid":120760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:20:50.000Z","msg":"自推兩下"},{"pid":"ea027531af38fed6990eb834597bad603e6dfc48","tid":1485909,"uid":120760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:24:30.000Z","msg":"自推三下"},{"pid":"fa7c3211d44b998eebd0ffd2ae0f128d7a255936","tid":1485909,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:25:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19130db0618d351398a3108cfe9c73d68fcd9de6","tid":1485909,"uid":120760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:26:20.000Z","msg":"自推四下"},{"pid":"cf29a74f8f719b62dea0e8a16c495d1e18347c03","tid":1485909,"uid":120760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:28:01.000Z","msg":"自推五下"},{"pid":"d8227b6882284a0bdfa80b8acfd6b1293a5bf205","tid":1485909,"uid":120760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:29:54.000Z","msg":"自推六下"},{"pid":"3dd7ee610000c67deb9095597f862047dc20fdeb","tid":1485909,"uid":261430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30742eaa97f72c744384dadfc87975430d92f14f","tid":1485909,"uid":50779,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:11:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:29:56.000Z","msg":"敢集會／遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" cl